threads.title: 820-3476 no power
threads.message:
Arrived with no liquid damage. All power rails are present but P1V05S0_PGOOD is only 0.104V and PPVCC_S0_CPU only 0.47V

Both enables  except P1V05S3_EN are present for U7600, no changes after replacing it.

What should be checked next??

threads.title: 820-3476 no power
threads.message:
Exact C7649 voltage?
Diode mode to ground?

Check/replace R/C7630 and R7631.

threads.title: 820-3476 no power
threads.message:
C7649  1.055v 0.090 diode

Replaced R/C7630 and R7631 

no change

threads.title: 820-3476 no power
threads.message: Remove R8164 and test the board.

threads.title: 820-3476 no power
threads.message:
PM_SLP_S3_BUF_L stays high?
If yes, remove Q8150 and test the board again.
